{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>《Optima》 是一款將運動、營養、睡眠與日常健康數據整合於一身的應用程式，目前正推出限時免費活動。它適合想要全面掌握身體狀況，卻厭倦在多個軟體間切換的使用者。無論你是健身愛好者還是追求健康生活的上班族，都能透過這款 App 輕鬆管理所有健康資訊，讓追求進步的過程變得更加井然有序且高效。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/460x460bb-75-14.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>一站式整合所有健康數據與運動計畫</h2>\n    <p>使用者能自訂專屬健身計畫，詳細記錄每組訓練的重量與次數，並透過 GPS 功能精確追蹤跑步路徑。飲食管理方面，支援條碼掃描快速輸入熱量與三充營養比例，同時能與 Apple Health 同步步數及心率數據。簡潔的介面提供直觀的趨勢分析圖表，幫助你從睡眠品質到水分攝取，全方位觀察自身的健康成長趨勢。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1242x2688bb-31-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1242x2688bb-32-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1242x2688bb-33-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1242x2688bb-34-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1242x2688bb-35-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/1242x2688bb-36-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <ul>\n      <li>應用名稱：optima: health tracker</li>\n      <li>應用類別：Health &amp; Fitness</li>\n      <li>下載位置：App Store</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-02T23:27:21.521405+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":376,"images":7,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}